cs.DL, cs.IR, cs.AI, cs.DB, cs.SI 

The paper discusses the use of metadata in library catalogs for the Semantic Web, which falls under the category of digital libraries (cs.DL). The paper also mentions the use of RDF and FRBR, which are commonly used in information retrieval (cs.IR) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) research. The proposed implementation for a repository of theses and dissertations involves database design (cs.DB) and potentially social network analysis (cs.SI) to reveal the academic network.
